snippet.title: Cricket 19: The official game of the Ashes accolades trailer
snippet.description:
Hi all! We have some great news to share! 

The critics love Cricket 19, and soon you will be playing it on PC - Cricket 19 launches on July 31 via Steam! Play along through all the excitement of the Ashes!
